  "Julai" - is an arcade flight shooter.  The action  takes  place  on
  Technogenic Planet. You can improve your ship and flying through the
  Thorns to earn a lot of points. The game is  designed  for  reaction
  and ardor.Key features of the game: Horizontal-endless  game  world;
  You can fly wherever you want (down,  horizontally,  upwards);  Each
  ship item affects its functionality; Any item  of the  ship  can  be
  attached or dropped via construction yard; Every item  of  the  ship
  can be taken as a bonus; If you catch the 'autopilot' bonus, you can
  fly  with  "autopilot";  There  are  various  types    of  opponents
  (fighters, drills which clinging to the ship, turret.
